- GLSceneLighting: tests normal lighting
- GLSceneNormal: test normal mapping shaders
- GLSceneShadow: tests shadow mapping 
- GLSceneParticles: tests updating the VBOs dynamically (drawing particles)
- GLSceneCometTail: as with GLSceneParticles it tests dynamic use of VBO, but in this case by drawing a tail to the path of the mouse pointer
